acceptance_criteria: pm health treats optional item-type directories as non-fatal by default while supporting explicit strict directory enforcement and deterministic diagnostics.
goal: External report remediation
objective: Reduce false-negative health failures
value: Health status reflects real integrity state
impact: Avoids noisy automation failures
outcome: Optional directory gaps no longer fail default health
why_now: Reported behavior currently marks healthy trackers as failed
