body: "Implements issue-report remediation for false-negative health status caused by missing optional directories (events/reminders/milestones/meetings).\n\nFollow-up scope: add pm health --strict-exit / --fail-on-warn behavior so automation can enforce non-zero exits when health warnings produce ok=false, while preserving default backward-compatible exit semantics."
